item.title: Quick Basic Updo
item.description:
Quick Basic Updo
Hey guys, Back to Basics! Here is a really quick hair tutorial (if your hair is pre-curled cough..lol). It's kind of messy so it looks laid back but it also has an elegant quality to it. It's really easy! Easy peasy ftw! I was getting ready to have dinner with the boyfriend and thought I'll film the quick hairstyle. It's so basic that I contemplated whether I should upload this ahh well, hope you guys still enjoy this quickie. You CAN do this hairstyle with straight hair but it must be straightened so hair is poker straight. However, I prefer this hairstyle with tousle waves because it looks softer. If your hair is naturally curly- this hairstyle will be ever quicker. I love to do my makeup whilst rollers are still on my head. Make most of time baby!! Time to prepare for Halloween tutorials (decided to actually participate this year lol). I'll also be concentrating on my comedy channel Bubbiosity. I miss making silly videos ^_^ Ok- off to make my 'Death Note book'. $20 on ebay? Psssh can make my own for under $3!!!! Much love Bubz xx _________________ Check out the Bubzbeauty Official Website.
